## MCP JSON for Roo Code etc

To use this in Roo Code, Cline etc use

"n8n-context7": {
      "url": "https://n8n.coolify.au/mcp/dafd56e8-ea19-43b7-b337-a5881c3bc541/sse",
      "alwaysAllow": [
        "call_context7_ai_agent"
      ]
    }

where the url is the the path that you get from the mcp server node in n8n
